For ROS, the /etc/hosts file should contain appropriate entries. 

For comm VM, it should contain the IP address for all other VMs and the OCU.
For OCU, it should contain the IP address of comm VM.
For all other VMs, they should contain IP address of all other VMs.

Note that the IP address should be of the private network between VMs. 

There needs to be firewall rules for all VMs and the OCU to prevent unauthorized access. 
There needs to be IPSec rules for all VMs and the OCU to authenticate IP packets.

